name: Up Up UFO
description:
Take The UFO Up And Up The UFO can only break through a block if the block below it is the same colour!

How many floors can you climb?

Created for the ScoreSpace Jam #9 game jam

I've added multiple control layouts. Take your pick and find what's most comfortable for you

Tap the key to move to that block. If you're on that block, you'll go up
